  <summary date="2021-02-19T19:37:42Z" status="Introduced in House">Saving America's Energy Future Act

This bill prohibits the Department of Agriculture and the Department of the Interior from declaring a moratorium on issuing new oil and gas leases and drill permits on certain federal lands. In addition, the bill prohibits the departments from declaring a moratorium on renewals of such permits.</summary>
